movie_title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
title: The film was great
review: I thought that the film was great and i can't wait for Episode II to come out in 2002. The lightsabre battles had been improved greatly from the originals and the special effects were brilliant. i recommend this film to anybody who wants a good day out at the cinema

title: Not that bad
review: The Mummy had some very good special effects and it was very loud which made me jump. but the storyline was not that spectacular and i didn't think that it was worth the money to go and see it. If you want my advice go and see it for the special effects but nothing else.
